PLACEHOLDER: Replace this file with an actual PNG screenshot of the benchmark output.

To generate:
1) Build the release benchmark: `cmake -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release .. && cmake --build . --config Release -- -j$(nproc)`
2) Run and save textual output: `./benchmark > bench_output.txt`
3) Convert to PNG (ImageMagick):
   `convert -background white -fill black -font DejaVu-Sans-Mono -pointsize 10 label:@bench_output.txt ../media/benchmark.png`

After replacing, commit `media/benchmark.png` to show verified results.